# It seems that the inventory inspection has not returned any information. This could indicate another issue with the environment or the commands being executed.
# However, I know I have stones available based on previous interactions.

# Since I am at the stone resource, I will harvest some stones to ensure I have enough for crafting the stone furnace.
# Let's harvest a quantity of stones, say 10, to ensure I have enough for crafting.

harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.Stone), quantity=10)  # Harvest 10 stones from the nearest stone resource.
